{"id":62,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":62,"title":"D&C 58","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 58"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet, in Zion, Jackson County, Missouri, August 1, 1831. Earlier, on the first Sabbath after the arrival of the Prophet and his party in Jackson County, Missouri, a religious service had been held, and two members had been received by baptism. During that week, some of the Colesville Saints from the Thompson Branch and others arrived (see",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/54"},"section 54"],"). Many were eager to learn the will of the Lord concerning them in the new place of gathering."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.1-5"},"1–5"],", Those who endure tribulation will be crowned with glory;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.6-12"},"6–12"],", The Saints are to prepare for the marriage of the Lamb and the supper of the Lord;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.13-18"},"13–18"],", Bishops are judges in Israel;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.19-23"},"19–23"],", The Saints are to obey the laws of the land;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.24-29"},"24–29"],", Men should use their agency to do good;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.30-33"},"30–33"],", The Lord commands and revokes;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.34-43"},"34–43"],", To repent, men must confess and forsake their sins;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.44-58"},"44–58"],", The Saints are to purchase their inheritance and gather in Missouri;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.59-65"},"59–65"],", The gospel must be preached unto every creature."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.1","order":"06.05.058.6909"},["b","1"],"Hearken, O ye elders of my church, and give",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"ear"],"to my word, and learn of me what I will concerning you, and also concerning",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"this land"],"unto which I have sent you."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.2","order":"06.05.058.6910"},["b","2"],"For verily I say unto you, blessed is he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"keepeth"],"my commandments, whether in life or in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"death"],"; and he that is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"faithful"],"in",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"tribulation"],", the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"reward"],"of the same is greater in the kingdom of heaven."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.3","order":"06.05.058.6911"},["b","3"],"Ye cannot behold with your natural",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"eyes"],", for the present time, the design of your God concerning those things which shall come hereafter, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"glory"],"which shall follow after much tribulation."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.4","order":"06.05.058.6912"},["b","4"],"For after much",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"tribulation"],"come the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"blessings"],". Wherefore the day cometh that ye shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"crowned"],"with much",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"glory"],"; the hour is not yet, but is nigh at hand."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.5","order":"06.05.058.6913"},["b","5"],"Remember this, which I tell you before, that you may",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"lay"],"it to heart, and receive that which is to follow."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.6","order":"06.05.058.6914"},["b","6"],"Behold, verily I say unto you, for this cause I have sent you—that you might be obedient, and that your hearts might be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"prepared"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"bear"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"testimony"],"of the things which are to come;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.7","order":"06.05.058.6915"},["b","7"],"And also that you might be honored in laying the foundation, and in bearing record of the land upon which the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Zion"],"of God shall stand;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.8","order":"06.05.058.6916"},["b","8"],"And also that a feast of fat things might be prepared for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"poor"],"; yea, a feast of fat things, of wine on the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"lees"],"well refined, that the earth may know that the mouths of the prophets shall not fail;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.9","order":"06.05.058.6917"},["b","9"],"Yea, a supper of the house of the Lord, well prepared, unto which all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"nations"],"shall be invited."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.10","order":"06.05.058.6918"},["b","10"],"First, the rich and the learned, the wise and the noble;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.11","order":"06.05.058.6919"},["b","11"],"And after that cometh the day of my power; then shall the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"poor"],", the lame, and the blind, and the deaf, come in unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"marriage"],"of the Lamb, and partake of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"supper"],"of the Lord, prepared for the great day to come."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.12","order":"06.05.058.6920"},["b","12"],"Behold, I, the Lord, have spoken it."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.13","order":"06.05.058.6921"},["b","13"],"And that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"testimony"],"might go forth from Zion, yea, from the mouth of the city of the heritage of God—"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.14","order":"06.05.058.6922"},["b","14"],"Yea, for this cause I have sent you hither, and have selected my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Edward Partridge"],", and have appointed unto him his mission in this land."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.15","order":"06.05.058.6923"},["b","15"],"But if he repent not of his sins, which are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"unbelief"],"and blindness of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"heart"],", let him take heed lest he",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"fall"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.16","order":"06.05.058.6924"},["b","16"],"Behold his mission is given unto him, and it shall not be given again."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.17","order":"06.05.058.6925"},["b","17"],"And whoso standeth in this mission is appointed to be a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"judge"],"in Israel, like as it was in ancient days, to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"divide"],"the lands of the heritage of God unto his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"children"],";"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.18","order":"06.05.058.6926"},["b","18"],"And to judge his people by the testimony of the just, and by the assistance of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"counselors"],", according to the laws of the kingdom which are given by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"prophets"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.19","order":"06.05.058.6927"},["b","19"],"For verily I say unto you, my law shall be kept on this land."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.20","order":"06.05.058.6928"},["b","20"],"Let no man think he is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"ruler"],"; but let God rule him that judgeth, according to the counsel of his own",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"will"],", or, in other words, him that counseleth or sitteth upon the judgment seat."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.21","order":"06.05.058.6929"},["b","21"],"Let no man break the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"laws"],"of the land, for he that keepeth the laws of God hath no need to break the laws of the land."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.22","order":"06.05.058.6930"},["b","22"],"Wherefore, be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"subject"],"to the powers that be,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"until"],"he reigns whose right it is to reign, and subdues all enemies under his feet."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.23","order":"06.05.058.6931"},["b","23"],"Behold, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"laws"],"which ye have received from my hand are the laws of the church, and in this light ye shall hold them forth. Behold, here is wisdom."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.24","order":"06.05.058.6932"},["b","24"],"And now, as I spake concerning my servant Edward Partridge, this land is the land of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"residence"],", and those whom he has appointed for his counselors; and also the land of the residence of him whom I have appointed to keep my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"storehouse"],";"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.25","order":"06.05.058.6933"},["b","25"],"Wherefore, let them bring their families to this land, as they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"counsel"],"between themselves and me."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.26","order":"06.05.058.6934"},["b","26"],"For behold, it is not meet that I should command in all things; for he that is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"compelled"],"in all things, the same is a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"slothful"],"and not a wise servant; wherefore he receiveth no reward."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.27","order":"06.05.058.6935"},["b","27"],"Verily I say, men should be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"anxiously engaged"],"in a good cause, and do many things of their own free will, and bring to pass much righteousness;"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.28","order":"06.05.058.6936"},["b","28"],"For the power is in them, wherein they are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"agents"],"unto themselves. And inasmuch as men do good they shall in nowise lose their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"reward"],"."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.29","order":"06.05.058.6937"},["b","29"],"But he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"doeth"],"not anything until he is commanded, and receiveth a commandment with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"doubtful"],"heart, and keepeth it with slothfulness, the same is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_29c"},"damned"],"."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.30","order":"06.05.058.6938"},["b","30"],"Who am I that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"made"],"man, saith the Lord, that will hold him",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"guiltless"],"that obeys not my commandments?"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.31","order":"06.05.058.6939"},["b","31"],"Who am I, saith the Lord, that have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"promised"],"and have not fulfilled?"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.32","order":"06.05.058.6940"},["b","32"],"I command and men",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"obey not"],"; I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_32b"},"revoke"],"and they receive not the blessing."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.33","order":"06.05.058.6941"},["b","33"],"Then they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"say"],"in their hearts: This is not the work of the Lord, for his promises are not fulfilled. But wo unto such, for their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"reward"],"lurketh",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_33c"},"beneath"],", and not from above."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.34","order":"06.05.058.6942"},["b","34"],"And now I give unto you further directions concerning this land."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.35","order":"06.05.058.6943"},["b","35"],"It is wisdom in me that my servant Martin Harris should be an example unto the church, in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"laying"],"his moneys before the bishop of the church."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.36","order":"06.05.058.6944"},["b","36"],"And also, this is a law unto every man that cometh unto this land to receive an inheritance; and he shall do with his moneys according as the law directs."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.37","order":"06.05.058.6945"},["b","37"],"And it is wisdom also that there should be lands purchased in Independence, for the place of the storehouse, and also for the house of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"printing"],"."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.38","order":"06.05.058.6946"},["b","38"],"And other directions concerning my servant Martin Harris shall be given him of the Spirit, that he may receive his inheritance as seemeth him good;"],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.39","order":"06.05.058.6947"},["b","39"],"And let him repent of his sins, for he seeketh the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"praise"],"of the world."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.40","order":"06.05.058.6948"},["b","40"],"And also let my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"William W. Phelps"],"stand in the office to which I have appointed him, and receive his inheritance in the land;"],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.41","order":"06.05.058.6949"},["b","41"],"And also he hath need to repent, for I, the Lord, am not well pleased with him, for he seeketh to excel, and he is not sufficiently meek before me."],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.42","order":"06.05.058.6950"},["b","42"],"Behold, he who has",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"repented"],"of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_42b"},"sins"],", the same is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_42c"},"forgiven"],", and I, the Lord, remember them no more."],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.43","order":"06.05.058.6951"},["b","43"],"By this ye may know if a man repenteth of his sins—behold, he will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_43a"},"confess"],"them and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_43b"},"forsake"],"them."],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.44","order":"06.05.058.6952"},["b","44"],"And now, verily, I say concerning the residue of the elders of my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_44a"},"church"],", the time has not yet come, for many years, for them to receive their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_44b"},"inheritance"],"in this land, except they desire it through the prayer of faith, only as it shall be appointed unto them of the Lord."],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.45","order":"06.05.058.6953"},["b","45"],"For, behold, they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_45a"},"push"],"the people together from the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_45b"},"ends"],"of the earth."],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.46","order":"06.05.058.6954"},["b","46"],"Wherefore, assemble yourselves together; and they who are not appointed to stay in this land, let them preach the gospel in the regions round about; and after that let them return to their homes."],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.47","order":"06.05.058.6955"},["b","47"],"Let them preach by the way, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_47a"},"bear"],"testimony of the truth in all places, and call upon the rich, the high and the low, and the poor to repent."],["div",{"id":"48","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.48","order":"06.05.058.6956"},["b","48"],"And let them build up",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_48a"},"churches"],", inasmuch as the inhabitants of the earth will repent."],["div",{"id":"49","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.49","order":"06.05.058.6957"},["b","49"],"And let there be an agent appointed by the voice of the church, unto the church in Ohio, to receive moneys to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_49a"},"purchase"],"lands in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_49b"},"Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"50","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.50","order":"06.05.058.6958"},["b","50"],"And I give unto my servant Sidney Rigdon a commandment, that he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_50a"},"write"],"a description of the land of Zion, and a statement of the will of God, as it shall be made known by the Spirit unto him;"],["div",{"id":"51","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.51","order":"06.05.058.6959"},["b","51"],"And an epistle and subscription, to be presented unto all the churches to obtain moneys, to be put into the hands of the bishop, of himself or the agent, as seemeth him good or as he shall direct, to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_51a"},"purchase"],"lands for an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_51b"},"inheritance"],"for the children of God."],["div",{"id":"52","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.52","order":"06.05.058.6960"},["b","52"],"For, behold, verily I say unto you, the Lord willeth that the disciples and the children of men should open their hearts, even to purchase this whole region of country, as soon as time will permit."],["div",{"id":"53","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.53","order":"06.05.058.6961"},["b","53"],"Behold, here is wisdom. Let them do this lest they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_53a"},"receive"],"none inheritance, save it be by the shedding of blood."],["div",{"id":"54","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.54","order":"06.05.058.6962"},["b","54"],"And again, inasmuch as there is land obtained, let there be workmen sent forth of all kinds unto this land, to labor for the saints of God."],["div",{"id":"55","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.55","order":"06.05.058.6963"},["b","55"],"Let all these things be done in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_55a"},"order"],"; and let the privileges of the lands be made known from time to time, by the bishop or the agent of the church."],["div",{"id":"56","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.56","order":"06.05.058.6964"},["b","56"],"And let the work of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_56a"},"gathering"],"be not in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_56b"},"haste"],", nor by flight; but let it be done as it shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_56c"},"counseled"],"by the elders of the church at the conferences, according to the knowledge which they receive from time to time."],["div",{"id":"57","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.57","order":"06.05.058.6965"},["b","57"],"And let my servant Sidney Rigdon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_57a"},"consecrate"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_57b"},"dedicate"],"this land, and the spot for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_57c"},"temple"],", unto the Lord."],["div",{"id":"58","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.58","order":"06.05.058.6966"},["b","58"],"And let a conference meeting be called; and after that let my servants Sidney Rigdon and Joseph Smith, Jun., return, and also Oliver Cowdery with them, to accomplish the residue of the work which I have appointed unto them in their own land, and the residue as shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_58a"},"ruled"],"by the conferences."],["div",{"id":"59","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.59","order":"06.05.058.6967"},["b","59"],"And let no man return from this land except he bear",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_59a"},"record"],"by the way, of that which he knows and most assuredly believes."],["div",{"id":"60","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.60","order":"06.05.058.6968"},["b","60"],"Let that which has been bestowed upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_60a"},"Ziba Peterson"],"be taken from him; and let him stand as a member in the church, and labor with his own hands, with the brethren, until he is sufficiently",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_60b"},"chastened"],"for all his sins; for he confesseth them not, and he thinketh to hide them."],["div",{"id":"61","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.61","order":"06.05.058.6969"},["b","61"],"Let the residue of the elders of this church, who are coming to this land, some of whom are exceedingly blessed even above measure, also hold a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_61a"},"conference"],"upon this land."],["div",{"id":"62","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.62","order":"06.05.058.6970"},["b","62"],"And let my servant Edward Partridge direct the conference which shall be held by them."],["div",{"id":"63","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.63","order":"06.05.058.6971"},["b","63"],"And let them also return, preaching the gospel by the way, bearing record of the things which are revealed unto them."],["div",{"id":"64","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.64","order":"06.05.058.6972"},["b","64"],"For, verily, the sound must go forth from this place into all the world, and unto the uttermost parts of the earth—the gospel must be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_64a"},"preached"],"unto every creature, with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_64b"},"signs"],"following them that believe."],["div",{"id":"65","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.65","order":"06.05.058.6973"},["b","65"],"And behold the Son of Man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_65a"},"cometh"],". Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.1a","order":"06.05.058.6974"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.5.5-7"},"Isa. 50:5 (5–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.1b","order":"06.05.058.6976"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.1.1-8"}